    <p>ABU DHABI • World cham­pion Lewis Hamil­ton, who has won six of his record seven ti­tles with Mercedes since join­ing in 2013, ended spec­u­la­tion about fu­ture in­ten­tions on Sun­day when he made clear he ex­pects to sign a new con­tract with the Sil­ver Ar­rows be­fore Christ­mas.</p>
    <p>The Bri­ton said talks with team chief Toto Wolff were likely to start in the next “cou­ple of weeks” and his plans was “to be here next year”.</p>


